#To color/colour with dye.

====Example====
"Dyed in the wool" a quality garment, where the dye has been applied before weaveing, typically making it longer lasting.
Also applied by analogy to people, "a dyed in the wool mysogenist" someone who always has been and always will be mysogenistic.

